posts.text: CodeJavaScript12(async function () { let res = await fetch("https://google.com") })();void function (){ console.log( "hello world!" )}(); bluma blue block KaTeX$\mathbf{Theorem \ 7.1. \ (Cauchy’s \ residue \ theorem).}$ Let G be a simply connected domain and let P $= \{a_1, . . . , a_n\} \subseteq$ G. Let $\gamma$ be a simple closed path in G surrounding $a_1, . . . , a_n$ with positive orientation. For f $\subseteq \mathcal{H}(G \ P)$ we have $$\int_{\gamma}{f\left( z \right) dz=2}\pi i\sum_{j=1}^n{\text{Res}\left( f,a_j \right)}$$ 中文我欲因之梦吴越，一夜飞度镜湖月。脚著谢公屐，身登青云梯。竹杖芒鞋轻胜马，谁怕？一蓑烟雨任平生。
